Library    OperatingSystem


*** Variables ***

${BUILD_ID}               ${EMPTY}
${SWITCH_TOKEN}           ${EMPTY}
${SWITCH_SECRET}          ${EMPTY}
${TEST_WIFI_SSID}         ${EMPTY}
${TEST_WIFI_PSWD}         ${EMPTY}
${DEVICE_TYPE}            ${EMPTY}
${JOB}                    ${EMPTY}
${LOGIN}                  ghaf
